    "content": {
      "text": "UNITED STATES OF AMERICA FLIGHT PROHIBITION AGAINST CERTAIN\nFLIGHTS IN THE TEHRAN FLIGHT INFORMATION REGION (FIR) (OIIX).\n14 CFR 91.1617 SPECIAL FEDERAL AVIATION REGULATION (SFAR) NO.\n117--PROHIBITION AGAINST CERTAIN FLIGHTS IN THE TEHRAN FLIGHT\nINFORMATION REGION (FIR) (OIIX) WAS PUBLISHED IN THE FEDERAL\nREGISTER ON 3 OCT 2024 AND WAS EFFECTIVE ON 3 OCT 2024. OPERATORS\nARE DIRECTED TO READ THE FULL CONTENT OF THE RULE.\nTHIS INFORMATION IS PROVIDED AT:\nHTTPS://WWW.FAA.GOV/AIR_TRAFFIC/PUBLICATIONS/US_RESTRICTIONS/"
